  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly familar, entirely novel, piece of technology, designed by Specialist Polo as part of their <span class=\"name name-technology\">loop research</span> efforts. It synchronises its vibrations with the underlying song of the universe, allowing it to reveal <span class=\"name name-stellar\">memory hotspots</span> within the loop.<br><br>Begin the <span class=\"name name-technology\">resonance alignment</span> process with <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一项非常熟悉，却又完全新颖的技术，由保罗专家设计，作为其<span class=\"name name-technology\">循环研究</span>工作的一部分。它将其振动与宇宙的底层声音同步，使其能够揭示循环中的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">记忆热点</span>。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始<span class=\"name name-technology\">共振校对</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "令人十分熟悉，卻完全創新的科技，由專家波羅所設計，用於<span class=\"name name-technology\">迴圈研究</span>。振動頻率和宇宙深處的歌聲同步，使其能夠在迴圈中發現<span class=\"name name-stellar\">記憶熱點</span>。<br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span> 開始<span class=\"name name-technology\">共振校準</span>。"
  },
